*Lisom* se često igraju deca. (Children often play with a kite.) 

*Lise* su slobodno letale po vazduhu. (The kites were freely flying in the air.) 

Mali Džo je *lisu* pustio da se dizala visoko. (Little Joe let his kite rise high.) 

*Lisa* je virila iznad oblaka. (The kite was soaring above the clouds.) 

Niko nije mogao da zaustavi *lisu*, koja se iznenada odvojila. (No one could stop the kite, which suddenly detached.)